{
  "stem": "27507.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was a way to find out the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think I lost my head probably more than the others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I probably run out first and then ran on the landing-- on the staircase landing-- and that was already too late to do anything, because already Ukrainian was there, and he shouted at us to go down.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all went down, and that means myself and two cousins of mine, who were older.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a girl of 16 and a boy of 18, 19, and my uncle who was still a bit older.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we all came out to the street, and then we were there right in front of the shop.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The shop was right in front next to us but, of course, it was locked and closed, and there was not way of getting in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we all had-- and it was a hot, hot day, very hot and sunny, and we all had to first to sit or even kneel, I think, on the-- on this pavement there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they were-- it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it probably was not as long as I remember it, but to me it was probably something like half an hour or 40 minutes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But to me it appeared absolute eternity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they shouted, to, and they surrounded everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was a long, long column of people, maybe-- maybe thousands of people whom they managed, and they surrounded us all with Ukrainians and some dogs and so on and police and Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody had a part in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But maybe I didn't think I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
